g/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2年都執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0999845716cc1716c7ba36911757a1a3ea617c93","tid":1182402,"uid":4798,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"唔係想打沉士氣，不過以家根本係頭痛醫頭，腳痛醫腳。<br />\n香港人根本就沉迷係「香港=中國」論，<br />\n由頭到尾都唔抗拒比中國統治，<br />\n反而十分抗拒有人提出/爭取獨立，明明可以各有各做/一齊合作，偏偏大部份人都只會奚落義士。<br />\n好啦，港獨撚比政府拉哂去坐監啦，<br />\n偏偏個班先係唯一一班肯同你衝肯同你搏嘅人，<br />\n以家淨番個班以泛民為主嘅所謂示威者，除左遊行（比盡佔領），<br />\n又肯為香港同自己嘅前途去到幾盡呢？<br />\n七十九日嘅佔領都迫唔到政府讓步，如果大家都只係諗住遊下行唱下歌就可以改變現實，我寧願負面啲乜都唔做，都唔想再哂時間/比假希望自己。"},{"pid":"e2f7f135fe18fa478f2b9650decffccc5df4cefc","tid":1182402,"uid":164980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb8a9777e3af2c7056bf02ef2d1874998bbe48b0","tid":1182402,"uid":78046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"一早已經倒數緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dfq60jF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfq60jF.png&h=ef5ccf03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"555f5e3f80cdd063d860496082906fba3d6c2fdb","tid":1182402,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"741b54b5440e36fe200a2ad1d733ab69a5455236","tid":1182402,"uid":112124,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d47447dd08f5851a2328427b36348d8679e4b19e","tid":1182402,"uid":163350,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"a8320cb176f413b2175aea0bb2d3e9e8252e1efc","tid":1182402,"uid":112124,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"遲又點？都要企出黎架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T07:17:49.000Z","msg":"唔試過 又點會知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://thumby.wisdomtoinspire.com/thumbs/lrg/4yK_4FMt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumby.wisdomtoinspire.co